{"tid":1139203,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA一線] 呢條女做fyp真係好勁~","createTime":"2019-05-05T05:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T11:36:27.000Z","uid":36084,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdc264241bf972aa12c47c51c905b03be6d325e","tid":1139203,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"38歲的關智斌（Kenny）昨午在IG發帖，自爆被操國語的女狂迷騷擾半年，日前更被對方踩上門夜闖其居住的大廈，令Kenny深感困擾，揚言擔心人身安全。不少粉絲叮囑偶像出入要小心；有人亦呼籲他快快報警備案！<br />\n<br />\n男子組合BOYZ成員Kenny已轉戰內地娛樂圈多年，他在13年與趙麗穎合作古裝劇《追魚傳奇》後爆紅，曾有指他拍一部長劇的酬金達3,000萬人民幣，身價不菲。此外，擁有Fit爆身形的Kenny經常在社交網大方騷爆肌照，成功吸納大量女粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n自覺人身安全受威脅<br />\n<br />\n不過，這位男神原來近日被女狂迷騷擾。昨午，Kenny在IG發千字文及CCTV截圖，照片中的女子被打格。他透露，前日被該名女子硬闖其居住的大廈，更自揭已被騷擾達半年，認真慘情。Kenny透露，本周二晚上突然收到其居住屋苑的保安員通知，有一位穿紅衣、拖着行李篋及說國語的女士出現在大廈門口，並且嘗試利用保安通話聯絡他及其鄰居，意圖闖入電梯大堂。Kenny留言︰「幸得盡責的屋苑保安人員阻止。遺憾的是，這已經不是第一次發生&hellip;&hellip;在這半年間，在我的社交平台一直也收到應該是這位女士的留言和圖片，內容帶着莫名奇妙的想像和威脅性的語氣。」<br />\n<br />\nKenny亦指，該狂迷竟然掌握很多他的個人資料，如地址、電話號碼、通訊帳號等，迫使他從今年初起把很多個人資料更新。Kenny特別在IG向該狂迷作公開呼籲︰「你的恐怖行為已經令我深深感到困擾，我開始擔心自己的人身安全。」他又強調，若這些騷擾情況持續，會考慮報警。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，Kenny的經理人霍汶希亦轉發帖文，呼籲粉絲不要打擾藝人的私生活。而網友都紛紛叫Kenny報警；有粉絲亦呼籲他出席活動時，要請私人保鑣，以策安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2341716/%E9%97%9C%E6%99%BA%E6%96%8C%E9%81%AD%E5%A5%B3%E7%8B%82%E8%BF%B7%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE%20%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%EF%B8%B0%E6%90%B5%E7%95%AA%E5%80%8B%E8%B2%BC%E8%BA%AB%E4%BF%9D%E9%91%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2341716%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2596%258C%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%258B%2582%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E6%2593%25BE%2520%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25EF%25B8%25B0%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%2595%25AA%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2591%25A3&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2yxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=aaaa3b82\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2341716/%E9%97%9C%E6%99%BA%E6%96%8C%E9%81%AD%E5%A5%B3%E7%8B%82%E8%BF%B7%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE%20%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%EF%B8%B0%E6%90%B5%E7%95%AA%E5%80%8B%E8%B2%BC%E8%BA%AB%E4%BF%9D%E9%91%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n做緊fyp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef90271860bf7a4010cb2fd49c7bf7c1e01147a","tid":1139203,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"佢癲啲定當年個劉華狂迷癲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a4b5ce9359424beb968bc1615a134f8e5f6420","tid":1139203,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ef90271860bf7a4010cb2fd49c7bf7c1e01147a","tid":1139203,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"佢癲啲定當年個劉華狂迷癲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"癲咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做緊fyp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa02b9d579be46842969d6db8a949bd2f9c411f","tid":1139203,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e9a2c0a58de81c0e536cfc05b38b718e75e101","tid":1139203,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5993597efb4129bae6b6bde5d53fb7adc3adc06","tid":1139203,"uid":216519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:36:27.000Z","msg":"比比鳥之前條女好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fb好多野睇"}]}